Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 小伊波 我去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 馬上帶兩位入座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 小真晝 我去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3位吧 請問吸煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在這打工很久了 卻還是只能接待女客
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做一半工作 給大家添麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待女性客人很完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 本來下決心今天一定要努力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦 小伊波 今天還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌補的機會還多得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該這樣 小伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊波…
